751
01:00:49,800 --> 01:00:53,420
[SPEAKER_04] ali nema smisla da svi razvijemo nekakve slične substave,

752
01:00:53,420 --> 01:00:54,920
[SPEAKER_04] ali tako da i to treba imati.

753
01:00:54,920 --> 01:00:59,380
[SPEAKER_09] Zahvaljujem. Da li, prije nego što dam lijeć,

754
01:00:59,380 --> 01:01:04,599
